title: Trinity - Paris Eyes - Get Out - Jazz Organ
description:
Trinity - Paris Eyes - Get Out - Jazz Organ

Trinity is a great swinging Swedish jazz organ trio, with the quite unusual set-up of organ, trumpet and drums.
Line-up is Andreas Hellkvist at the organ, Karl Olandersson, trumpet and Ali Djeridi, drums.

List of included albums:
2010 Paris Eyes
2011 Get Out

----------

MP3 format. All songs are tagged by the book.
